quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,123,ae ehley imaan! apne nazdeek ke ( rehne walay ) kafiroon se jung karo aur chahiye ke woh tum mein sakhti ( yani mehnat o qowat jung ) maloom karen. aur jaan rakho ke khuda parhaiz gaaron ke sath hai
9,124,aur jab koi sourat nazil hoti hai to baaz munhafiq (istehzaa karte aur ) puchhte ke is sourat ne tum mein se kis ka imaan ziyadakiya hai. so jo imaan walay hain un ka imaan to ziyadakiya aur woh khush hotay hain
9,125,"aur jin ke dilon mein marz hai, un ke haq mein khbs par khbs ziyadakiya aur woh marey bhi to kafir ke kafir"
9,126,kiya yeh dekhte nahi ke yeh har saal aik ya do baar bulaa mein phansa diye jatay hain phir bhi tauba nahi karte aur nah nasiyaat pakarte hain
9,127,aur jab koi sourat nazil hoti hai aik dosray ki janib dekhnay lagtay hain ( aur puchhte hain ke ) bhala tumhe koi daikhta hai phir phir jatay hain. khuda ne un ke dilon ko phair rakha hai kyunkay yeh aisay log hain ke samajh se kaam nahi letay
9,128,( logo ) tumahray paas tum hi mein se aik paighambar aeye hain. tumhari takleef un ko giran maloom hoti hai aur tumhari bhalai ke khwahish mand hain aur mominon par nihayat shafqat karne walay ( aur ) meharban hain
9,129,phir agar yeh log phir jayen ( aur nah manen ) to keh do ke khuda mujhe kifayat karta hai is ke siwa koi mabood nahi isi par mera bharosa hai aur wohi arsh azeem ka maalik hai
